Dear first years,

Hockey Freshie Schroeter (UG & PG freshers) details are as follows:

Date: 26th August
Time: 5 PM Onwards
Venue: Institute Hockey Ground

A team of 8 players (6 + 2 subs) with name and roll number from the same
